<DIV2 N="67" TYPE="chapter">
<PB N="292" REF="293">
<HEAD>CHAP. LXVII.</HEAD>
<HEAD TYPE="sub">The longe&s;t and the la&s;t.</HEAD>
<P>THE nature of this vi&s;it had &s;oftened every
heart, and &s;addened every countenance;
and they walked in &s;olemn &s;ilence to the other
